name: Advaita
description:
Just One Eternal Unholy Spirit in existence.
We are like waves on the ocean, looking for the ocean, longing to be part of it.
But the wave was always the ocean, from the very beginning, even in its seeking! It’s the ocean looking for itself. Even within the ocean’s failure to find itself it is still the ocean; every wave is one hundred per cent water.
.
